A project to transform MPI applications to use GOAL library.
==============================================================
Sriram Aananthakrishnan
aananthakris1@llnl.gov
09/04/2012

* This project uses to ROSE to transform MPI applications
to use the GOAL library. The transformation uses the dataflow
framework in ROSE for analysis. 
* Currently, the transformation is guided by annotations. These
will be replaced by program analysis information.

Package Contents
------------------
1. src
2. tests

src - code to build the translator
tests - example MPI test codes

Features
-----------
1. Inserts GOAL library headers into the MPI application
2. Inserts the Init and finalize statements of GOAL library

